00:36:47.460 --> 00:36:51.340
able to sustain meat production
for a growing

00:36:51.340 --> 00:36:53.720
population by then.

00:36:53.720 --> 00:36:56.530
So we're at a juncture where
we can either choose to be

00:36:56.530 --> 00:36:59.860
innovative in solving this
issue, or we can be dragged

00:36:59.860 --> 00:37:02.350
there by necessity, by the
collapse of our environment

00:37:02.350 --> 00:37:05.330
and ecosystems and animal
cruelty just

00:37:05.330 --> 00:37:06.570
being out of control.

00:37:06.570 --> 00:37:09.550
Now, thankfully there are some
real pioneers that are jumping

00:37:09.550 --> 00:37:12.065
