We have Russell Simmons founder
of Def Jam Records,

00:37:23.350 --> 00:37:26.830
who has adopted a plant-based
diet, former President Bill

00:37:26.830 --> 00:37:29.640
Clinton, who is an outspoken
advocate for plant-based

00:37:29.640 --> 00:37:33.490
eating, and then we have
billionaire Steve Wynn, from

00:37:33.490 --> 00:37:37.500
Las Vegas, who is also jumping
on the veggie bandwagon.

00:37:37.500 --> 00:37:39.600
It's not just some of the
brightest minds and

00:37:39.600 --> 00:37:42.840
entrepreneurs, but we have
sports athletes.

00:37:42.840 --> 00:37:46.910
The Houston Texan Arian Foster,
who is a proud vegan

00:37:46.910 --> 00:37:50.700
now as well, showing that we
sacrifice nothing, not our

00:37:50.700 --> 00:37:53.440
strength, not our health,
by eliminating meat.

00:37:53.440 --> 00:37:55.020
We gain everything.

00:37:55.020 --> 00:37:58.190
And we're starting to see the
new generation of college

00:37:58.190 --> 00:38:01.990
students embracing this idea
and the need as well.

